[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **Vulnerability Details**                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Endpoint**: `/check_service`                                               [32m│[0m
