[32m│[0m - Flask app.py receives JSON POST requests                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Constructs command: `./check_service.sh {service_name}`                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Executes via `subprocess.check_output(command, shell=True)`                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The bash script (`check_service.sh`) uses `getopts` to parse arguments     [32m│[0m
