[32m│[0m - Filters these characters: `&`, `|`, `$`, `;`, `\n`, `\r`, backticks        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Does NOT filter: hyphens (-), angle brackets (<, >), quotes                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **The Vulnerability**:                                                       [32m│[0m
